             was indicted for <rs id="t18060917-38-off200" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18060917-38-off200" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18060917-38-off200" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing a lamb, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18060917-38-victim304" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Weekly
                  <interp inst="t18060917-38-victim304" type="surname" value="Weekly"></interp>
